==References==
* The [use] link taking you to your campsite is a reference to the [[wikipedia:World of Warcraft|World of Warcraft]] Hearthstone items that teleport the player back to their current lodgings.
** Amusingly, if one were to use [[Steal Monster's Heart]] to extract the middle letter of "Hearthstone", one would be left with the name of this item.

